features.text:
#Third Floor

#Havent yet decided for sure what my plans are for this floor.. Im considering on using this floor as a means of showing up and coming artists works to help gain visibility on them. Still working on this idea.

#Second Floor

#The second floor includes more of my favorite pieces similar to the 1st floor but many of the pieces on this floor already have listing prices.. Again, many pieces are long form motion design so to see the FULL length of these pieces you have to click on them to view full version.

#First Floor

#This floor contains some of my favorite NFTs, many of which are long form Motion design, so in order to see the FULL NFT you'll have to click the link on them.  


#Many of the pieces on this floor do not have a listing price however i consider selling for the right price.
